Package: daphne
Title: This package creates nice looking regression tables.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: "Lisa Rein <lisaerein@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: This package creates nice looking regression tables. There are
    several functions for different types of models. Each function returns a
    dataframe and also prints an html table by default for use in R markdown
    documents.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    xtable htmlTable
License: CC0
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    knitr htmlTable
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1

